{"type":"text","timestamp":1773352321107,"sessionID":"ses_31bfcf566ffeX54k1gNGv0ej46","part":{"id":"prt_ce408f004001KSiFtGktkg2o9Q","sessionID":"ses_31bfcf566ffeX54k1gNGv0ej46","messageID":"msg_ce408e8c8001qYxnY1DQp1a6qI","type":"text","text":"Good. The launch command already uses `config.browser.enabled` from the config object — so for launch, the `--browser` flag should override `config.browser.enabled` similarly to how verify does it. Now let me implement the changes.\n\n### Step 1: Add `--browser` flag to CLIArgs and parseArgs in `src/index.ts`","time":{"start":1773352321106,"end":1773352321106}}}
